 the order 3mn peak to peak, they\nshould influence past, present and future observations providing further\nconstraints on the planet internal structure and atmosphere.}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2011 12:38:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
